1
00:00:11,387 --> 00:00:15,456
(Seven years ago)

2
00:00:20,399 --> 00:00:23,160
How dare you newbie
wield your blade against me?

3
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:25,920
I saw you asking
the Liang family's farmer for bribery.

4
00:00:26,079 --> 00:00:27,000
Give the money back.

5
00:00:34,719 --> 00:00:37,200
I can do whatever I want here.

6
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:39,920
This is the Huaizhou Prefecture.

7
00:00:40,159 --> 00:00:44,960
Know the rules before you talk or act.

8
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:47,600
If you dare to cause me trouble again,

9
00:00:47,799 --> 00:00:49,960
my men won't let you off so easily.

10
00:00:50,399 --> 00:00:52,560
You lawless people.

11
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:57,000
I'm going to Prefect Chen now.

12
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:03,560
Shen Mu, right? You've got some nerves.

13
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:07,040
Our Prefect Chen
has been overwhelmed by the case

14
00:01:07,719 --> 00:01:10,159
between Miss Lin and the Yanyu Tower.

15
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,640
He has some anger to vent.

16
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:17,824
Go ask for a good beating. Let's go.

17
00:02:57,128 --> 00:03:02,184
=Faithful=
(Adapted from the novel "Faithful")

18
00:03:02,895 --> 00:03:06,072
=Episode 7, Chapter 4, Part 1=
(Mrs. Wu Finds Mr. Wu a Fine Concubine)

19
00:03:29,287 --> 00:03:32,167
Rulan, it's all my fault.

20
00:03:33,366 --> 00:03:36,206
If I hadn't sent you
to that so-called Yanyu Tower,

21
00:03:36,686 --> 00:03:38,607
you wouldn't have
suffered such misfortune.

22
00:03:39,007 --> 00:03:40,607
I am the one to blame.

23
00:03:41,007 --> 00:03:42,206
No, Mother.

24
00:03:43,047 --> 00:03:46,327
I loved embroidery
and asked you to send me there.

25
00:03:46,806 --> 00:03:48,047
Let me kill that bad man!

26
00:03:48,206 --> 00:03:50,246
Are you trying
to stir things up even more?

27
00:03:50,407 --> 00:03:52,567
Father, Wu Lian crossed the line!

28
00:03:53,806 --> 00:03:54,727
My little sister...

29
00:03:58,246 --> 00:04:00,926
Lin's Clinic sent us a message that

30
00:04:01,407 --> 00:04:05,966
(Mr. Lin)
they won't take Lin Lang in just yet.

31
00:04:11,167 --> 00:04:12,526
Is it because of me?

32
00:04:19,047 --> 00:04:22,047
I'm sorry you're implicated
because of me.

33
00:04:23,326 --> 00:04:25,926
And I got our family store closed.

34
00:04:26,207 --> 00:04:27,366
Don't talk nonsense.

35
00:04:28,087 --> 00:04:30,287
I don't need a mentor like that.

36
00:04:31,287 --> 00:04:36,246
Gossip is a fearful thing.
It's normal for Mr. Lin to hesitate.

37
00:04:45,087 --> 00:04:47,486
Rulan, don't overthink.

38
00:04:48,087 --> 00:04:49,566
Father and Mother will protect you.

39
00:04:50,246 --> 00:04:51,326
And I'm here for you.

40
00:05:07,486 --> 00:05:08,566
What are you doing?

41
00:05:08,566 --> 00:05:10,167
Proposing, obviously.

42
00:05:10,566 --> 00:05:12,967
Mr. Lin, I've done
matchmaking for almost

43
00:05:13,126 --> 00:05:14,446
all the respected families

44
00:05:14,686 --> 00:05:16,207
in Huaizhou Prefecture.

45
00:05:16,446 --> 00:05:19,126
I'm here in person only

46
00:05:19,326 --> 00:05:20,767
because Mrs. Wu insists on it.

47
00:05:20,926 --> 00:05:22,647
Listen. Rulan is not getting married.

48
00:05:23,006 --> 00:05:24,287
Get those things back.

49
00:05:24,407 --> 00:05:26,607
How can you force a girl to get married?

50
00:05:26,967 --> 00:05:28,407
With all due respect,

51
00:05:28,607 --> 00:05:31,326
not everyone can be so lucky.

52
00:05:31,566 --> 00:05:34,006
Not even a virgin girl gets to

53
00:05:34,207 --> 00:05:35,806
marry Mr. Wu so easily,

54
00:05:36,006 --> 00:05:38,486
let alone your daughter.

55
00:05:38,767 --> 00:05:39,647
You...

56
00:05:40,087 --> 00:05:41,967
Mr. Lin, as you can see,

57
00:05:42,126 --> 00:05:44,926
the Wu family offers betrothal gifts
of the highest standard.

58
00:05:45,126 --> 00:05:47,126
Who's so generous to a concubine?

59
00:05:47,727 --> 00:05:49,087
Mrs. Wu is just kind enough

60
00:05:49,566 --> 00:05:51,126
to help save your daughter's reputation.

61
00:05:51,326 --> 00:05:52,926
Am I right?

62
00:05:53,087 --> 00:05:54,847
- Yeah.
- Totally.

63
00:05:55,047 --> 00:05:56,207
If I were Mrs. Wu...

64
00:05:57,847 --> 00:06:00,806
Come on, carry the things inside. Go.

65
00:06:00,926 --> 00:06:01,767
Who dares to come in?

66
00:06:02,167 --> 00:06:04,047
Mr. Lin, just wait for the wedding.

67
00:06:04,207 --> 00:06:05,407
Get lost! Take them away!

68
00:06:05,566 --> 00:06:07,926
Nobody wants your betrothal gifts!

69
00:06:08,366 --> 00:06:09,486
Who dares to come in?

70
00:06:09,767 --> 00:06:11,207
You have a death wish?

71
00:06:13,527 --> 00:06:15,126
Come and try it.

72
00:06:15,926 --> 00:06:18,566
Ungrateful people.
You'd better not regret it.

73
00:06:18,727 --> 00:06:19,806
Get lost!

74
00:06:20,126 --> 00:06:21,486
Let's go.

75
00:06:21,727 --> 00:06:23,527
So ungrateful.

76
00:06:25,087 --> 00:06:27,806
What are you looking at? Get lost!

77
00:06:29,727 --> 00:06:31,126
The Wu family prepared so many gifts.

78
00:06:31,287 --> 00:06:32,967
It's good enough for your girl.

79
00:06:33,806 --> 00:06:35,287
But you drove them away.

80
00:06:36,246 --> 00:06:37,366
Father, let's go in.

81
00:06:37,767 --> 00:06:38,607
Let's go.

82
00:06:41,368 --> 00:06:42,648
(Lin's Pharmacy)

83
00:06:55,647 --> 00:06:58,047
Rulan, we're here for you.

84
00:06:58,607 --> 00:07:01,727
In the worst-case scenario,
we'll sustain you forever.

85
00:07:14,967 --> 00:07:16,760
You're back?

86
00:07:18,207 --> 00:07:19,407
Pick carefully.

87
00:07:20,886 --> 00:07:21,767
Give it to me!

88
00:07:22,126 --> 00:07:23,087
Or I'll beat you up.

89
00:07:23,326 --> 00:07:24,886
I don't even have a penny.

90
00:07:25,047 --> 00:07:26,006
I beat you!

91
00:07:27,847 --> 00:07:28,886
Wan, you're back.

92
00:07:29,727 --> 00:07:30,926
Want to sit in my room?

93
00:07:31,087 --> 00:07:33,047
I have just steamed some buns. Try some.

94
00:07:33,246 --> 00:07:34,446
No, thanks, Mrs. Yang.

95
00:07:34,727 --> 00:07:36,167
Give it to me!

96
00:07:36,486 --> 00:07:38,006
I know

97
00:07:38,167 --> 00:07:39,207
you're hiding it!

98
00:07:39,607 --> 00:07:41,207
Give it to me!

99
00:07:41,967 --> 00:07:44,647
I remember you have
a fine bracelet in your dowry.

100
00:07:44,847 --> 00:07:46,486
Where did you hide it?

101
00:07:46,727 --> 00:07:49,287
You've traded all my dowry
for wine over the years.

102
00:07:49,486 --> 00:07:51,407
What bracelet do I have left?

103
00:07:52,006 --> 00:07:54,647
You even gave away
half of your ancestral house.

104
00:07:54,847 --> 00:07:55,727
How are we...

105
00:07:55,886 --> 00:07:56,886
Get lost!

106
00:07:57,047 --> 00:07:58,712
Mother.

107
00:08:00,366 --> 00:08:01,607
(Mrs. Meng)
Another loser!

108
00:08:01,847 --> 00:08:05,407
(Mr. Meng)
Your mother sent you to Yanyu Tower!

109
00:08:05,566 --> 00:08:07,087
It's time to pay for it.

110
00:08:07,326 --> 00:08:08,486
What are you doing?

111
00:08:09,847 --> 00:08:12,287
Look at your sour faces!

112
00:08:13,207 --> 00:08:14,686
Our family has been jinxed

113
00:08:14,967 --> 00:08:17,366
and lost all the fortune because of you.

114
00:08:17,806 --> 00:08:18,727
Mother.

115
00:08:19,686 --> 00:08:21,486
Are you trying to drive me crazy?

116
00:08:21,686 --> 00:08:22,527
Bad luck.

117
00:08:32,566 --> 00:08:33,686
What are you doing?

118
00:08:33,846 --> 00:08:34,926
Get lost.

119
00:08:34,926 --> 00:08:36,206
Mother.

120
00:08:36,206 --> 00:08:37,086
Listen to me.

121
00:08:37,326 --> 00:08:40,287
I won't let you off
until you give me that bracelet.

122
00:08:53,487 --> 00:08:57,287
Wan, you're my only hope.

123
00:08:57,966 --> 00:08:59,446
You must work hard.

124
00:09:00,686 --> 00:09:02,007
Your father will surely die

125
00:09:02,606 --> 00:09:05,407
in a few years
if he keeps drinking like this.

126
00:09:06,127 --> 00:09:07,686
The best decision I've made

127
00:09:08,047 --> 00:09:10,047
is to send you to Yanyu Tower.

128
00:09:11,767 --> 00:09:14,566
Work hard and master the skill.

129
00:09:15,086 --> 00:09:17,367
Marry a nice guy.

130
00:09:18,606 --> 00:09:20,767
Then we have hope in life.

131
00:09:25,326 --> 00:09:27,966
Why did you come home today?

132
00:09:33,086 --> 00:09:35,326
Did you do something wrong there?

133
00:09:35,806 --> 00:09:38,686
Many things happened there these days.

134
00:09:39,127 --> 00:09:41,606
Many parents took their daughters home.

135
00:09:42,527 --> 00:09:45,127
So our teacher stopped the lessons.

136
00:09:45,326 --> 00:09:47,606
Because of Lin Rulan's incident?

137
00:09:48,287 --> 00:09:50,127
It's no big deal.

138
00:09:50,446 --> 00:09:53,767
The Wu family sent betrothal gifts
to the Lin family today.

139
00:09:55,726 --> 00:09:56,647
What did you say?

140
00:09:56,846 --> 00:10:00,247
That girl would be lucky
to marry into the Wu family.

141
00:10:01,007 --> 00:10:02,206
Did they say yes?

142
00:10:02,806 --> 00:10:05,007
They drove the matchmaker away.

143
00:10:05,367 --> 00:10:07,926
I bet they're just
trying to ask for more.

144
00:10:08,566 --> 00:10:10,086
They'll end up with nothing.

145
00:10:10,926 --> 00:10:14,407
Look at you.
You're not any worse than Lin Rulan.

146
00:10:14,926 --> 00:10:16,647
Why aren't you capable of that?

147
00:10:16,887 --> 00:10:18,767
My silly girl.

148
00:10:19,127 --> 00:10:20,326
I'll be right back, Mother.

149
00:10:20,846 --> 00:10:22,446
Where are you going?

150
00:10:24,127 --> 00:10:26,407
Lin Rulan, come out!

151
00:10:27,007 --> 00:10:28,167
I know you're in there.

152
00:10:28,686 --> 00:10:31,367
Lin Rulan, come out.

153
00:10:32,287 --> 00:10:33,784
Lin Rulan.

154
00:10:34,456 --> 00:10:35,806
What are you doing?

155
00:10:35,926 --> 00:10:37,086
What am I doing?

156
00:10:37,767 --> 00:10:39,647
Why don't you ask your friend
what she's doing?

157
00:10:40,086 --> 00:10:41,127
She slandered Mr. Wu

158
00:10:41,407 --> 00:10:43,127
just to marry him.

159
00:10:43,487 --> 00:10:45,367
Now, her scheme worked.

160
00:10:46,127 --> 00:10:47,686
The Wu family sent a matchmaker here.

161
00:10:48,287 --> 00:10:49,206
She doesn't deserve it!

162
00:10:49,446 --> 00:10:51,647
Wu Lian did this to cover his tracks.

163
00:10:52,446 --> 00:10:54,487
Besides, they drove the matchmaker away.

164
00:10:54,726 --> 00:10:57,726
So pretentious.
She's just playing hard to get.

165
00:10:58,487 --> 00:10:59,606
Totally shameless.

166
00:10:59,926 --> 00:11:01,926
Why am I wasting my time
with her sidekick?

167
00:11:02,127 --> 00:11:03,846
Go away. Lin Rulan.

168
00:11:05,167 --> 00:11:07,127
Go ahead if you want to marry Mr. Wu.

169
00:11:07,966 --> 00:11:09,606
But I won't let you tarnish

170
00:11:10,047 --> 00:11:11,167
Rulan's reputation.

171
00:11:11,326 --> 00:11:12,686
I'm tarnishing her reputation?

172
00:11:13,446 --> 00:11:15,007
She has no reputation.

173
00:11:18,287 --> 00:11:19,206
Rulan.

174
00:11:20,606 --> 00:11:23,566
Get lost or I'll teach you a lesson.

175
00:11:24,287 --> 00:11:26,487
I don't have anything to lose now.

176
00:11:26,887 --> 00:11:30,086
Try me. Get lost.

177
00:11:30,887 --> 00:11:33,606
Lin Rulan, don't be so cocky.

178
00:11:34,407 --> 00:11:36,326
I'll wait to enjoy your misery.

179
00:11:40,926 --> 00:11:43,446
Rulan, is it true?

180
00:11:44,446 --> 00:11:45,767
He sent you betrothal gifts?

181
00:11:48,206 --> 00:11:49,966
How can he be so shameless?

182
00:11:51,175 --> 00:11:52,696
Rulan.

183
00:11:54,343 --> 00:11:55,744
Rulan.

184
00:12:01,103 --> 00:12:05,463
I've been looking for you. What's wrong?

185
00:12:06,304 --> 00:12:07,264
What do you want?

186
00:12:08,223 --> 00:12:09,784
The first day
of the lunar month is coming.

187
00:12:10,184 --> 00:12:11,264
Didn't we agree

188
00:12:11,503 --> 00:12:13,264
to burn incense at the Fuyuan Temple?

189
00:12:13,784 --> 00:12:14,944
I came to ask you

190
00:12:15,144 --> 00:12:17,264
what snacks to prepare.

191
00:12:17,743 --> 00:12:20,024
I'm not in the mood for that.

192
00:12:23,223 --> 00:12:24,064
Mr. Wu.

193
00:12:30,184 --> 00:12:31,024
Mr. Wu.

194
00:12:32,144 --> 00:12:35,144
Are you really marrying Lin Rulan?

195
00:12:37,784 --> 00:12:41,264
Go back to practice.
Your skill is deteriorating.

196
00:12:57,144 --> 00:12:59,823
(Huaizhou Prefecture Yamen)
Everyone's talking about that case.

197
00:13:00,144 --> 00:13:05,184
Have you heard the storytelling?
It was thrilling.

198
00:13:05,544 --> 00:13:06,424
You can do better.

199
00:13:06,743 --> 00:13:08,544
What's the fun of the storytelling?

200
00:13:08,743 --> 00:13:11,503
Wouldn't it be more exciting

201
00:13:11,664 --> 00:13:14,304
to hear it from the lady herself?

202
00:13:14,664 --> 00:13:17,703
Get to work. You guys,
we're going to the Lin's Pharmacy.

203
00:13:17,944 --> 00:13:21,223
Lin's Pharmacy?
Are we arresting Miss Lin?

204
00:13:21,944 --> 00:13:22,823
Prefect Chen told us

205
00:13:23,264 --> 00:13:25,823
- to bring her here.
- Let's go.

206
00:13:26,024 --> 00:13:27,304
Sorry.

207
00:13:27,944 --> 00:13:29,784
The granny who makes pancakes
was in trouble.

208
00:13:30,223 --> 00:13:33,304
I drove away those hooligans
and got delayed.

209
00:13:33,583 --> 00:13:35,424
A newbie wants to be a hero?

210
00:13:35,623 --> 00:13:37,784
Alright, come with us.

211
00:13:40,623 --> 00:13:43,343
I won't let you off
if you bring me food late again.

212
00:13:48,612 --> 00:13:52,463
(Lin's Pharmacy)

213
00:13:52,463 --> 00:13:53,976
Open up.

214
00:13:55,544 --> 00:13:56,632
Open up.

215
00:13:57,184 --> 00:13:58,840
Who is it?

216
00:13:59,064 --> 00:14:00,863
Coming. Just a second.

217
00:14:01,024 --> 00:14:03,103
- Open up.
- Coming. Wait.

218
00:14:05,343 --> 00:14:06,184
W-What are you doing?

219
00:14:06,343 --> 00:14:07,904
What's wrong, sir?

220
00:14:08,223 --> 00:14:09,823
What brought you here?

221
00:14:09,983 --> 00:14:12,223
We're working on a case.
Get Lin Rulan here.

222
00:14:12,384 --> 00:14:14,200
I'm here.

223
00:14:16,503 --> 00:14:18,784
We're looking into your case
against Wu Lian.

224
00:14:19,064 --> 00:14:20,623
Come with us to the Yamen.

225
00:14:20,983 --> 00:14:22,904
Wait, where is Captain Liu?

226
00:14:23,103 --> 00:14:24,583
You know Captain Liu?

227
00:14:24,823 --> 00:14:26,863
He's put in jail. Nobody told you?

228
00:14:27,184 --> 00:14:28,703
Cut the crap. Let's go.

229
00:14:28,944 --> 00:14:31,343
Sir, can I come with my little sister?

230
00:14:31,583 --> 00:14:32,544
You're irrelevant.

231
00:14:32,784 --> 00:14:36,223
Prefect Chen only told us
to bring Lin Rulan back. Let's go.

232
00:14:36,784 --> 00:14:37,944
- Rulan.
- Go.

233
00:14:38,384 --> 00:14:40,064
- Rulan.
- Go.

234
00:14:48,904 --> 00:14:49,823
Go.

235
00:14:49,823 --> 00:14:50,743
Rulan.

236
00:14:50,904 --> 00:14:53,103
Rulan.

237
00:14:53,264 --> 00:14:55,784
Rulan.

238
00:14:59,424 --> 00:15:00,784
Miss, are you cold?

239
00:15:01,463 --> 00:15:03,703
Would you like me to warm you up?

240
00:15:05,743 --> 00:15:07,983
She's not Yan'er in Yanchun House.

241
00:15:08,384 --> 00:15:09,743
She may sue you.

242
00:15:10,623 --> 00:15:11,784
Girls in Yanchun House

243
00:15:11,983 --> 00:15:13,823
are entertainers, not courtesans.

244
00:15:14,823 --> 00:15:16,424
She's no match for them.

245
00:15:16,983 --> 00:15:18,223
I strongly disagree.

246
00:15:18,863 --> 00:15:21,144
Miss Lin has fairer skin

247
00:15:21,544 --> 00:15:23,944
than the most popular girl
in Yanchun House,

248
00:15:24,503 --> 00:15:26,304
just like girls in Xiaoxiang House.

249
00:15:40,823 --> 00:15:41,703
Sit.

250
00:15:42,544 --> 00:15:43,784
I'd like to see Prefect Chen.

251
00:15:46,184 --> 00:15:48,064
Prefect Chen has tons of work.

252
00:15:48,623 --> 00:15:50,304
We're not distracting him.

253
00:15:51,944 --> 00:15:52,983
Sit.

254
00:15:56,024 --> 00:15:57,664
You filed a lawsuit against Wu Lian.

255
00:15:58,024 --> 00:16:00,304
So you have to tell us everything

256
00:16:00,544 --> 00:16:01,944
in detail

257
00:16:02,144 --> 00:16:04,064
for us to keep a record.

258
00:16:05,544 --> 00:16:06,424
Go ahead.

259
00:16:07,304 --> 00:16:11,823
How did Wu Lian assault you?
Give us the details.

260
00:16:12,784 --> 00:16:14,944
We can't afford to miss out

261
00:16:15,103 --> 00:16:16,343
on any important detail.

262
00:16:27,784 --> 00:16:28,703
Go ahead.

263
00:16:31,983 --> 00:16:33,184
Go ahead.

264
00:16:43,304 --> 00:16:46,264
I was sewing that night.

265
00:16:47,863 --> 00:16:49,583
Wu Lian suddenly came into my room

266
00:16:51,583 --> 00:16:54,304
and grabbed my hand from behind.

267
00:16:57,784 --> 00:16:58,664
What are you doing?

268
00:17:02,264 --> 00:17:03,463
Easy.

269
00:17:04,824 --> 00:17:06,904
We have to confirm every detail.

270
00:17:07,543 --> 00:17:09,944
