while undressing me,

276
00:17:46,344 --> 00:17:51,904
and pushing me onto the bed.

277
00:17:52,584 --> 00:17:54,584
Louder. I can't hear you.

278
00:17:55,904 --> 00:17:58,223
Do you hear him? Louder.

279
00:17:59,743 --> 00:18:03,223
What did Wu Lian do
after he pushed you onto the bed?

280
