but I just couldn't.

288
00:18:38,144 --> 00:18:39,783
How come?

289
00:18:44,303 --> 00:18:46,344
Was it like this?

290
00:18:50,503 --> 00:18:52,463
Now you're pretending to be a virgin?

291
00:18:56,223 --> 00:18:59,344
Mr. Zhou, Prefect Chen
only told us to solve the case,

292
00:19:00,584 --> 00:19:02,184
not to interrogate her.

293
00:19:03,624 --> 00:19:06,743
Who do you think you are, newbie?

294
00:19:06,944 --> 00:19:07,824
You learned

295
00:19:08,624 --> 00:19:10,503
to take pity on women before anything.

296
00:19:12,904 --> 00:19:15,344
Don't you see the teapot is empty?

297
00:19:15,824 --> 00:19:19,783
Go fetch some water. Go.

298
00:19:31,104 --> 00:19:32,624
Come on now.

299
00:19:53,223 --> 00:19:54,223
Captain Qian.

300
00:19:55,184 --> 00:19:56,424
Take her to be inspected.

301
00:19:59,664 --> 00:20:01,904
Go away. What are you doing?

302
00:20:02,584 --> 00:20:03,503
Step aside.

303
00:20:03,743 --> 00:20:06,223
Get in.

304
00:20:11,824 --> 00:20:12,944
Get undressed.

305
00:20:15,263 --> 00:20:18,624
What are you waiting for?
Should I do it for you?

306
00:20:21,144 --> 00:20:22,384
Why should I get undressed?

307
00:20:22,824 --> 00:20:24,864
A woman who claims
to have been assaulted

308
00:20:25,424 --> 00:20:27,503
should be inspected, of course.

309
00:20:27,783 --> 00:20:29,303
Otherwise, how do we know

310
00:20:29,503 --> 00:20:31,584
if you're telling the truth?

311
00:20:33,104 --> 00:20:35,824
Ma'am, can you tell them to leave?

312
00:20:36,104 --> 00:20:37,624
Or we can go to the inner room.

313
00:20:38,344 --> 00:20:39,624
I will collaborate.

314
00:20:39,904 --> 00:20:41,783
You're not a virgin girl.

315
00:20:42,023 --> 00:20:45,303
Why so pretentious? Hurry up.

316
00:20:46,303 --> 00:20:49,783
Ma'am, you're also a woman.
Please show mercy.

317
00:20:49,983 --> 00:20:51,824
Please. I beg you.

318
00:20:52,463 --> 00:20:55,104
It's fine if you don't
want to be undressed.

319
00:20:55,463 --> 00:20:58,584
Withdraw the lawsuit
and you'll be spared the trouble.

320
00:21:00,543 --> 00:21:02,463
No, I can't withdraw the lawsuit.

321
00:21:03,783 --> 00:21:05,743
Then you can't blame me for this.

322
00:21:06,063 --> 00:21:07,983
Someone, help her.

323
00:21:09,424 --> 00:21:10,463
Get lost, guys.

324
00:21:13,023 --> 00:21:14,104
Help!

325
00:21:18,184 --> 00:21:19,223
Let go of me!

326
00:21:30,664 --> 00:21:33,344
Shen Mu, are you out of your mind?

327
00:21:33,983 --> 00:21:35,584
Hands off her.

328
00:21:37,783 --> 00:21:38,904
Hands off her.

329
00:21:51,584 --> 00:21:52,543
Get out.

330
00:22:01,624 --> 00:22:02,584
Get out.

331
00:22:05,783 --> 00:22:07,783
Alright, get out.

332
00:22:34,783 --> 00:22:36,184
Stay here with Ma'am.

333
00:22:53,624 --> 00:22:54,664
Prefect Chen.

334
00:22:55,824 --> 00:22:57,344
How's it going?

335
00:22:58,824 --> 00:23:00,983
Zhou Yi and those guys
have gone too far.

336
00:23:01,944 --> 00:23:03,824
It was too much even for me.

337
00:23:04,144 --> 00:23:07,463
People should know their limits.

338
00:23:08,144 --> 00:23:10,503
Otherwise, they'll harm
others and themselves.

339
00:23:11,104 --> 00:23:13,384
That girl won't last.

340
00:23:13,824 --> 00:23:16,023
I bet she's going to resign soon.

341
00:23:17,864 --> 00:23:20,624
I don't care what Lin Rulan wants.

342
00:23:21,303 --> 00:23:23,543
But I can't let anything go wrong

343
00:23:23,584 --> 00:23:24,624
for Mrs. Ning.

344
00:23:25,144 --> 00:23:28,424
Don't let that girl
tarnish Mr. Wu's reputation.

345
00:23:28,983 --> 00:23:30,023
Yes.

346
00:23:47,463 --> 00:23:51,063
Ma'am, you've inspected me.

347
00:23:51,824 --> 00:23:54,263
Does it serve as evidence?

348
00:23:55,783 --> 00:23:59,063
I'll report to Prefect Chen accordingly.

349
00:24:00,344 --> 00:24:03,344
It's true that
you're no longer a virgin girl.

350
00:24:04,983 --> 00:24:09,664
But I haven't seen any signs of a tear.

351
00:24:10,384 --> 00:24:14,904
Therefore, we can conclude

352
00:24:15,144 --> 00:24:17,543
that you either did it voluntarily

353
00:24:17,904 --> 00:24:21,384
or took the initiative to lure Mr. Wu.

354
00:24:25,063 --> 00:24:28,624
Ma'am, that's not true.

355
00:24:29,223 --> 00:24:30,303
No?

356
00:24:30,463 --> 00:24:31,344
No.

357
00:24:32,584 --> 00:24:36,783
I've seen plenty of young ladies
who would do anything

358
00:24:37,503 --> 00:24:39,664
to marry into
wealthy families just like you.

359
00:24:40,184 --> 00:24:43,184
I suggest you stop it
before it's too late.

360
00:24:43,664 --> 00:24:49,743
Do not end up losing everything.

361
00:25:20,424 --> 00:25:23,543
Miss Lin, we don't have
women's clothes in the Yamen.

362
00:25:23,904 --> 00:25:26,184
It's a new gown. Please make do with it.

363
00:26:07,584 --> 00:26:08,424
Thank you.

364
00:26:12,023 --> 00:26:14,703
I'll take you to the clothes shop
on South Street.

365
00:26:16,344 --> 00:26:18,864
No need. I can go by myself.

366
00:26:19,584 --> 00:26:22,664
I'm just worried that
you'd run into Mr. Zhou on the way.

367
00:26:29,303 --> 00:26:33,344
Alright, thank you.

368
00:26:38,184 --> 00:26:39,223
Who says she can leave?

369
00:26:40,424 --> 00:26:41,824
Miss Lin is not a suspect.

370
00:26:42,624 --> 00:26:43,983
You've questioned her

371
00:26:44,424 --> 00:26:45,743
and inspected her.

372
00:26:46,463 --> 00:26:48,743
Mr. Qian, is there anything else?

373
00:26:48,944 --> 00:26:50,328
You...

374
00:26:51,944 --> 00:26:53,783
Alright, let her go.

375
00:27:05,783 --> 00:27:07,263
Why did you let her go?

376
00:27:08,664 --> 00:27:10,463
People saw her coming to the Yamen.

377
00:27:10,864 --> 00:27:12,703
Are we going to keep her here?

378
00:27:13,023 --> 00:27:14,543
But Prefect Chen told us...

379
00:27:16,303 --> 00:27:18,344
That Lin Rulan is a hard nut to crack.

380
00:27:19,104 --> 00:27:20,864
I guess we can't make her back down

381
00:27:21,063 --> 00:27:22,144
like this.

382
00:27:22,743 --> 00:27:24,584
Let's think of something else.

383
00:27:26,543 --> 00:27:28,664
Shen Mu is the one to blame.

384
00:27:30,584 --> 00:27:32,463
Can't you even tame your people?

385
00:27:43,303 --> 00:27:44,424
I'll get this one.

386
00:27:44,983 --> 00:27:45,944
Ten wen.

387
00:27:51,743 --> 00:27:53,703
I didn't bring money.

388
00:28:09,783 --> 00:28:12,184
This is my token and my uniform.

389
00:28:12,743 --> 00:28:13,703
(Huaizhou Prefecture)
They are for collateral.

390
00:28:14,824 --> 00:28:15,703
Is that fine?

391
00:28:19,063 --> 00:28:20,792
Sure.

392
00:28:22,303 --> 00:28:23,303
Thank you, sir.

393
00:28:30,983 --> 00:28:35,104
I'll ask my brother
to pay for the clothes.

394
00:28:37,184 --> 00:28:39,743
Are you going to keep suing Mr. Wu?

395
00:28:43,344 --> 00:28:45,664
I know they're giving me a hard time,

396
00:28:46,144 --> 00:28:47,344
so I can withdraw it.

397
00:28:48,384 --> 00:28:52,424
I thought Yamen officials
would do me justice.

398
00:28:54,983 --> 00:28:58,223
What they did convinced me
to fight to the end.

399
00:28:59,223 --> 00:29:02,223
If I can't find justice here,
I'll go to the capital.

400
00:29:02,944 --> 00:29:05,424
I'm sure there is justice somewhere.

401
00:29:09,664 --> 00:29:12,983
Maybe you can find yourself a litigator.

402
00:29:13,983 --> 00:29:18,144
I heard that
some litigators are really good.

403
00:29:21,703 --> 00:29:22,543
Why?

404
00:29:26,424 --> 00:29:27,944
Everyone in Huaizhou Prefecture

405
00:29:28,463 --> 00:29:29,983
thinks I'm a shameless girl

406
00:29:31,184 --> 00:29:32,904
who has seduced Wu Lian

407
00:29:33,503 --> 00:29:36,104
to marry into the Wu family.

408
00:29:38,824 --> 00:29:40,223
Why did you help me

409
00:29:40,824 --> 00:29:43,223
and even turned against your colleagues?

410
00:29:44,624 --> 00:29:47,463
Don't you find me filthy?

411
00:29:48,344 --> 00:29:51,503
I didn't think so much.

412
00:29:52,384 --> 00:29:55,503
I just thought that
they shouldn't mistreat you.

413
00:30:02,104 --> 00:30:05,023
Thank you.

414
00:30:12,503 --> 00:30:13,584
Because I believe you.

415
00:30:15,983 --> 00:30:18,144
I believe what you said.

416
00:30:19,624 --> 00:30:20,703
I don't think a lady

417
00:30:20,904 --> 00:30:22,944
would lie to tarnish her reputation.

418
00:30:24,263 --> 00:30:25,543
I don't find you filthy.

419
00:30:26,664 --> 00:30:30,584
Those who have done
the evil deed are the filthy ones.

420
00:30:42,664 --> 00:30:43,624
What's your name?

421
00:30:44,584 --> 00:30:45,463
Shen Mu.

422
00:30:49,424 --> 00:30:52,184
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

423
00:31:23,864 --> 00:31:26,424
Rulan, you're back.

424
00:31:27,104 --> 00:31:28,263
Did they give you a hard time?

425
00:31:29,223 --> 00:31:31,864
Rulan, why did you get changed?

426
00:31:32,983 --> 00:31:34,664
They didn't do something to you, right?

427
00:31:36,864 --> 00:31:38,184
They didn't do anything.

428
00:31:39,543 --> 00:31:43,463
I got changed
because my clothes got dirty.

429
00:31:44,664 --> 00:31:45,904
Stop being worried.

430
00:31:48,184 --> 00:31:50,223
I'm a bit tired. I'll get some rest.

431
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:53,344
Rulan.

432
00:31:53,344 --> 00:31:54,776
Lin Lang.

433
00:31:56,983 --> 00:31:58,184
What should we do?

434
00:33:27,424 --> 00:33:28,463
What do you want?

435
00:33:28,543 --> 00:33:30,743
Weren't you a tough guy when you

436
00:33:31,463 --> 00:33:32,944
saved the beauty earlier?

437
00:33:46,104 --> 00:33:47,063
I won't use my blade.

438
00:33:47,983 --> 00:33:51,063
We all work here. Don't push me.

439
00:34:08,463 --> 00:34:10,103
Kowtow to me.

440
00:34:10,424 --> 00:34:11,463
And I'll let you off.

441
00:34:12,143 --> 00:34:14,904
You used to work
for that villain Liu Xin.

442
00:34:16,463 --> 00:34:17,864
Now that he's in jail,

443
00:34:19,063 --> 00:34:23,103
I'd be so terrified if I were you.

444
00:34:23,264 --> 00:34:24,183
Shut up!

445
00:34:34,864 --> 00:34:36,143
Mark my words.

446
00:34:37,304 --> 00:34:38,904
If you dare to cross me again,

447
00:34:39,264 --> 00:34:41,264
I swear I'll kill you.

448
00:34:44,623 --> 00:34:48,583
Let's go. To Yanchun House. My treat.

449
00:35:25,983 --> 00:35:28,063
It's the first day
of the lunar month tomorrow.

450
00:35:28,663 --> 00:35:29,864
On the first day of each lunar month,

451
00:35:30,143 --> 00:35:32,784
the head monk at Fuyuan Temple
would read people's fortunes.

452
00:35:33,183 --> 00:35:36,183
I'll ask him to bless you
with a good marriage.

453
00:35:38,103 --> 00:35:39,063
What's wrong?

454
00:35:41,344 --> 00:35:43,983
I'm dizzy. I want to go to bed.

455
00:35:44,183 --> 00:35:46,663
Alright, your father is still out.

456
00:35:46,983 --> 00:35:48,103
Rest well.

457
00:35:59,183 --> 00:36:00,344
The first day of the lunar month.

458
00:36:47,623 --> 00:36:48,704
Don't touch it.

459
00:36:51,344 --> 00:36:52,344
Haven't I told you

460
00:36:53,623 --> 00:36:57,344
not to touch
any embroidery in this study?

461
00:36:57,983 --> 00:37:00,224
Master, please forgive us.

462
00:37:00,784 --> 00:37:01,983
- Leave me alone.
- Yes.

463
00:37:51,424 --> 00:37:53,583
Isn't Lanxin in charge of the study?

464
00:37:53,864 --> 00:37:55,183
Why is someone else on duty?

465
00:37:55,744 --> 00:37:58,384
I heard that
something happened at her home.

466
00:37:58,583 --> 00:38:00,224
Mr. Wu let her go with some money.

467
00:38:00,583 --> 00:38:03,663
So sudden? Yesterday afternoon,
she was telling me

468
00:38:03,864 --> 00:38:04,864
to go shopping

469
00:38:05,103 --> 00:38:06,704
with her once we're free.

470
00:38:06,983 --> 00:38:08,304
Are you idling about?

471
00:38:09,384 --> 00:38:10,304
Get back to work.

472
00:38:10,384 --> 00:38:11,304
Yes.

473
00:38:21,944 --> 00:38:24,183
Sir, how much can I get with these?

474
00:38:27,623 --> 00:38:30,463
These are common items.
Two guan at most.

475
00:38:34,623 --> 00:38:36,183
Fine. Two guan is fine.

476
00:38:40,183 --> 00:38:41,023
Here.

477
00:38:52,103 --> 00:38:54,304
Are you Mr. Qian?

478
00:38:56,543 --> 00:38:58,384
I heard that you studied law

479
00:38:58,784 --> 00:39:00,824
and have won many lawsuits.

480
00:39:01,983 --> 00:39:04,384
Will you take on my case?

481
00:39:07,344 --> 00:39:08,304
Who are you?

482
00:39:08,503 --> 00:39:10,503
I'm Lin Rulan. Some days ago...

483
00:39:11,183 --> 00:39:15,543
You were the one who sued
Mr. Wu from Yanyu Tower?

484
00:39:17,623 --> 00:39:19,384
Go away. This is a school.

485
00:39:19,543 --> 00:39:22,103
It's a place for education.
Don't tarnish my reputation.

486
00:39:23,304 --> 00:39:24,784
But you haven't heard me out.

487
00:39:25,824 --> 00:39:27,623
If we go on talking,

488
00:39:27,983 --> 00:39:30,424
I'm afraid you'd sue me as well.

489
00:39:39,983 --> 00:39:40,824
Go away.

490
00:39:41,103 --> 00:39:43,424
If I represent
a shameless person like you,

491
00:39:43,583 --> 00:39:45,784
I'll sabotage my reputation.

492
00:39:48,583 --> 00:39:49,824
You will help me for real?

493
00:39:50,063 --> 00:39:52,264
Of course, why don't we

494
00:39:52,503 --> 00:39:55,183
talk about the case in detail at night?

495
00:39:55,944 --> 00:39:58,503
I'm sure we can figure things out.

496
00:40:09,983 --> 00:40:11,103
Mr. Li.

497
00:40:43,784 --> 00:40:45,384
Stop it.

498
00:40:49,384 --> 00:40:50,264
Stop it.

499
00:40:54,583 --> 00:40:55,424
Let's go.

500
00:41:14,663 --> 00:41:16,663
Sir, are you fine?

501
00:41:17,183 --> 00:41:19,463
I'm fine, Miss.

502
00:41:26,520 --> 00:41:28,696
(A Litigator with Ten Years of Experiences)

503
00:41:33,344 --> 00:41:37,503
Will you help me with my lawsuit?

504
00:41:37,663 --> 00:41:40,864
Miss, didn't you see what happened?

505
00:41:41,583 --> 00:41:42,864
Yes, I did.

506
00:41:42,864 --> 00:41:44,264
And you dare to hire me?

507
00:41:46,143 --> 00:41:48,824
Should I tell you about my case first?

508
00:41:49,183 --> 00:41:51,623
I've heard about it.

509
00:41:52,224 --> 00:41:53,744
I was right outside the Yamen

510
00:41:54,023 --> 00:41:55,944
when you filed the lawsuit.

511
00:41:56,784 --> 00:41:59,224
So will you help me?

512
00:41:59,623 --> 00:42:03,424
I only have one question
before I take on a case.

513
00:42:04,224 --> 00:42:06,063
Were you telling

514
00:42:06,304 --> 00:42:09,744
the whole and absolute truth that day?

515
00:42:09,904 --> 00:42:12,663
Yes. I swear on my life.

516
00:42:15,384 --> 00:42:19,904
Alright, then I'll take on the case.

517
00:42:20,983 --> 00:42:22,224
Really?

518
00:42:22,224 --> 00:42:23,768
Really.

519
00:42:27,623 --> 00:42:29,264
Please take the money.

520
00:42:30,983 --> 00:42:32,904
Alright.

521
00:42:32,904 --> 00:42:37,063
Miss, I'll wait for you at the teahouse
the day after tomorrow.

522
00:42:37,543 --> 00:42:40,784
Tell me everything once we meet.

523
00:42:41,704 --> 00:42:43,448
Alright.

524
00:42:51,264 --> 00:42:53,663
I've found a litigator
who's willing to represent me.

525
00:42:54,023 --> 00:42:55,424
Thank you for your advice.

526
00:42:56,143 --> 00:42:57,983
Justice will be done.

527
00:42:58,264 --> 00:43:00,463
I'm sure you'll clear your name.

528
00:43:02,623 --> 00:43:04,224
Ever since I filed the lawsuit,

529
00:43:05,463 --> 00:43:08,224
you're the only one
who's been supportive.

530
00:43:08,663 --> 00:43:09,704
I'm a Yamen officer.

531
00:43:10,023 --> 00:43:11,304
This is my job.

532
00:43:11,463 --> 00:43:12,983
You don't have to thank me.

533
00:43:13,983 --> 00:43:16,663
But it's bound to be an arduous journey.

534
00:43:17,183 --> 00:43:18,304
Be very careful.

535
00:43:19,543 --> 00:43:21,503
Okay, I will.

536
00:43:23,103 --> 00:43:27,023
I'll treat you to a drink once I win.

537
00:43:28,103 --> 00:43:29,583
Alright.

538
00:43:29,583 --> 00:43:31,143
Adulterous couple.

